---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Licensing - ByteLite" 
  description="ByteLite compression technology licensing options. Personal, Family, and Enterprise solutions for 1GB to 15 bytes compression. Transparent pricing for revolutionary technology."
>

  <section class="pricing-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Choose Your Plan</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        All plans include access to the ByteLite Application when available, 
        priority updates on Deep Kore Neural Recursion, and direct contribution to humanity's technological advancement.
      </p>

      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <!-- Personal Plan -->
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <div class="plan-header">
            <h3>Personal</h3>
            <div class="price">
              <span class="amount">$10</span>
              <span class="period">/month</span>
            </div>
            <div class="annual-price">or $99.99/year (save 17%)</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>1 Individual User</li>
            <li>1 Account</li>
            <li>1 System</li>
            <li>ByteLite Application Access</li>
            <li>Deep Kore Updates</li>
            <li>Email Support</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/subscribe" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Family Plan -->
        <div class="pricing-card featured">
          <div class="badge">Most Popular</div>
          <div class="plan-header">
            <h3>Family</h3>
            <div class="price">
              <span class="amount">$50</span>
              <span class="period">/month</span>
            </div>
            <div class="annual-price">or $499/year (save 17%)</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>10 Individual Users</li>
            <li>10 Accounts</li>
            <li>10 Systems</li>
            <li>ByteLite Application Access</li>
            <li>Deep Kore Updates</li>
            <li>Priority Email Support</li>
            <li>Family Management Dashboard</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/subscribe" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Enterprise Plan -->
        <div class="pricing-card enterprise">
          <div class="plan-header">
            <h3>Professional Enterprise</h3>
            <div class="price">
              <span class="amount">50%</span>
              <span class="period">of savings</span>
            </div>
            <div class="annual-price">No savings = No cost</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>Unlimited Users & Systems</li>
            <li>Self-Reporting API Integration</li>
            <li>Assigned Enterprise Auditor</li>
            <li>Annual Checksum Verification</li>
            <li>99.99%+ Typical Savings</li>
            <li>Direct Line Support</li>
            <li>Custom Integration</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Sales</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Enterprise Details -->
      <div class="enterprise-details">
        <h3>Enterprise Solution Details</h3>
        <div class="detail-grid">
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h4>Fair Usage Model</h4>
            <p>
              Pay only 50% of your realized cost savings. With ByteLite achieving 99.99%+ compression rates, 
              your savings are substantial. Example: Save $100 in storage/transmission → Pay $50 in licensing.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h4>Security & Compliance</h4>
            <p>
              Enterprise solutions integrate self-reporting to ByteLite LLC API for security and transparency. 
              Annual checksum verification ensures reporting software integrity.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h4>Dedicated Support</h4>
            <p>
              Each enterprise client receives an assigned Enterprise Solution Auditor for reporting verification, 
              application updates, and ongoing optimization consultation.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h4>Trust & Innovation</h4>
            <p>
              We trust our clients to help fund ByteLite LLC ventures. Your licensing fees directly support 
              groundbreaking technologies for the greater good of humanity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .pricing-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-darker);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .pricing-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .pricing-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .pricing-card.enterprise {
    border-color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
    padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .plan-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
  }

  .plan-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .amount {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .period {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .annual-price {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .features li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .features li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #00B8E6;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .enterprise-details {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .enterprise-details h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .detail-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .detail-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .detail-card:hover {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .detail-card h4 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .detail-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .pricing-card.featured {
      transform: none;
    }
  }
</style>